'''Leon Wadham''' is a New Zealand actor. He has portrayed the original [[Númenóreans|Númenórean]] character [[Kemen (The Rings of Power)|Kemen]] in Amazon's ''[[The Lord of the Rings: The Rings of Power]]'' series.<ref>{{webcite|author=The Lord of the Rings on Prime|articleurl=https://twitter.com/LOTRonPrime/status/15474182711415603214|articlename=Leon Wadham is Kemen. #TheRingsOfPower|dated=14 July 2022|website=[https://twitter.com Twitter]|accessed=5 February 2023}}</ref>
